    "1) Describe how to link numerous sites to a VPC?\n",
    "\n",
    "Ans:\n",
    "We can link numerous sites to a VPC through \"AWS VPN CloudHub\" which provides a secure communication between sites. This enables your remote sites to communicate with each other, along with the VPC.\n",
    "It works on hub-and-spoke model and can be used with or without a VPC. This design is suitable for multiple branch offices. \n",
    "One thing to note is that IP address range shouldn't be overlapping.\n"
   ]
  },
